close_reason: "Implemented a structured stdout sink, retained masked API key/password output, passed 838 tests with exact 100/100/100/100 coverage, passed 273 help checks and all release/security/history gates, and recorded the exact-head CodeQL follow-up for default-branch verification."
body: "Exact merged-head CodeQL alert #10 reports js/clear-text-logging at src/commands/config.ts:29. Although current payload builders mask apiKey and userPassword, a generic console.log sink accepts unknown payloads and permits future accidental secret disclosure. Replace it with the CLI structured stdout channel, retain formatting contracts, add regression coverage, and verify the alert closes on the new default-branch head."
